The paper deals with information embedding (watermarking) in covertexts, which is a topic related to information theory (cs.IT). The use of multiple-access attack channels is also a topic related to multimedia (cs.MM) and cryptography (cs.CR). The study of achievable embedding rates and distortion levels involves optimization and mathematical analysis, which are topics related to data structures (cs.DS) and machine learning (cs.LG).
